'''英國國家課程評量'''（National Curriculum assessments）為一系列的教育評估測驗，又名為 '''Sats'''<ref>[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/politics/education/primaryeducation/3199156/Sats-for-14-year-olds-abolished-Teachers-and-parents-praise-decision.html Sats for 14-year-olds abolished: Teachers and parents praise decision]</ref> 或是 '''SATs'''（詳見名稱部分）<ref name="banburyguardian">{{Cite web |url=http://www.banburyguardian.co.uk/news/Headteacher-welcomes-end-of-SATs.4595469.jp |title=Headteacher welcomes end of SATs |access-date=2015-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081018221731/http://www.banburyguardian.co.uk/news/Headteacher-welcomes-end-of-SATs.4595469.jp |archive-date=2008-10-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> ，為英國教育單位評估學童在學校的表現評量。測驗方式包含教師評估以及學生的測驗表現。本評量與同名的美國大學入學申請測驗「[[SAT|SAT]]」（學術評估測試）並無關連。

== 歷史 ==
本測驗約從1991~1998年開始施測<ref name="Sentinel">{{Cite web|title = The Sentinel|url = http://www.stokesentinel.co.uk/National-SATs-proved-controversial-introduced-19-years-ago/story-12485991-detail/story.html|website = {{url|stokesentinel.co.uk/|accessdate=9}} May 2015|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150924125401/http://www.stokesentinel.co.uk/National-SATs-proved-controversial-introduced-19-years-ago/story-12485991-detail/story.html|archivedate = 2015-09-24}}</ref> ，用於7歲，11歲以及14歲的學童，了解學生的學習程度。

之後取消14歲的測驗，而7歲的測驗改由教師評估。<ref name="Sentinel"/> 在2002年到2005年間，這些測驗逐漸在威爾斯地區淘汰。<ref name="Sentinel"/>

